{"word":"Assurance","slug":"assurance","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Assurance</b> Produced by faith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=3&verse=12'>Eph 3:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Ti 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=10&verse=22'>Heb 10:22</a><br/> Made full by hope<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=11'>Heb 6:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=6&verse=19'>Heb 6:19</a><br/> Confirmed by love<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=14'>1Jn 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=19'>1Jn 3:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=4&verse=18'>1Jn 4:18</a><br/> Is the effect of righteousness<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=32&verse=17'>Isa 32:17</a><br/> Is abundant in the understanding of the gospel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=2&verse=2'>Col 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=5'>1Th 1:5</a><br/> Saints privileged to have, assurance of:<br/> - Their election<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=4&verse=3'>Psa 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=4'>1Th 1:4</a> <br/> - Their redemption<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=19&verse=25'>Job 19:25</a> <br/> - Their adoption<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=16'>Rom 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Jn 3:2</a> <br/> - Their salvation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=12&verse=2'>Isa 12:2</a> <br/> - Their eternal life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=5&verse=13'>1Jn 5:13</a> <br/> - The unalienable love of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=8&verse=39'>Rom 8:39</a> <br/> - Union with God and Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=6&verse=15'>1Co 6:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=13&verse=5'>2Co 13:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=5&verse=30'>Eph 5:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=2&verse=5'>1Jn 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=4&verse=13'>1Jn 4:13</a> <br/> - Peace with God by Christ<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=5&verse=1'>Rom 5:1</a> <br/> - Preservation<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=3&verse=6'>Psa 3:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=9'>Psa 8:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=27&verse=5'>Psa 27:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=46&verse=3'>Psa 46:3</a> <br/> - Answers to prayer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=22'>1Jn 3:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=5&verse=15'>1Jn 5:15</a> <br/> - Comfort in affliction<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73&verse=26'>Psa 73:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=18'>Luk 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=4&verse=10'>2Co 4:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=4&verse=18'>2Co 4:18</a> <br/> - Continuance in grace<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=1&verse=6'>Phi 1:6</a> <br/> - A support in death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=23&verse=4'>Psa 23:4</a> <br/> - A glorious resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=19&verse=26'>Job 19:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=17&verse=15'>Psa 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=21'>Phi 3:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=62&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Jn 3:2</a> <br/> - A kingdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=28'>Heb 12:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=5&verse=10'>Rev 5:10</a> <br/> - A crown<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=8'>2Ti 4:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=1&verse=12'>Jas 1:12</a> <br/> - Saints give diligence to attain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=61&chapter=1&verse=11'>2Pe 1:11</a> <br/> - Strive to maintain<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=3&verse=14'>Heb 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=3&verse=18'>Heb 3:18</a> <br/> - Confident hope in God restores<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=42&verse=11'>Psa 42:11</a> <br/> Exemplified by:<br/> - David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=23&verse=4'>Psa 23:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73&verse=26'>Psa 73:26</a> <br/> - Paul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Ti 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=4&verse=18'>2Ti 4:18</a><br/><a href='S:Faith'>Faith</a> "}]}